      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>Correspondents include: publishers D. Bogue and Charles
         Tilt, and authors George Mills ( 
         <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">Beggar's Benison</title>) and John
         Wight ( 
         <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">Humbug for the Million</title>)</p>
    </scopecontent>
